name: james (@james@strangeobject.space)
summary:
You may remember I had my autism assessment last week on Wednesday. 

I was told I’d receive the report today or tomorrow morning and I’d have a feedback session via video call tomorrow at 1pm.

I have sent two emails since then to ask for confirmation of appointment and link to said video call.

No response.

Anyway I have come to the end of my assessment of my assessor and I hereby declare he is not autistic.
